<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٩٢ - وَقَالَ كُرَيْبٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>انْطَلَقَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> مِنْ الْمَدِينَةِ لِخَمْسٍ بَقِينَ مِنْ ذِي الْقَعْدَةِ، وَقَدِمَ مَكَّةَ لِأَرْبَعِ لَيَالٍ خَلَوْنَ مِنْ ذِي الْحِجَّةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
